<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="author" content="Pro-Logic" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1" />
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes" />

    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all" href="pro-logic/fonts/font-awesome.min.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="all" href="pro-logic/stylesheet/style.css" />

    <script type="text/javascript" src="pro-logic/javascript/jquery-1.12.2.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="pro-logic/javascript/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="pro-logic/javascript/site.js"></script>

    <title>Pro-Logic</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section id="header-container">
      <header id="header">
        <a id="logo" href="<%= ENV['PROLOGIC_URL'] %>">
          <img src="pro-logic/images/logo.png" />
        </a>
        <a id="phone" href="tel:61242979797"><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> +61 2 4297 9797</a>

        <!-- Menu -->
        <nav id="nav">
          <ul id="menu">
            <li><a href="#banner-container">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about-container">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#services-container">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#cashback">Cashback</a></li>
            <li><a href="#loyalty">Loyalty Programs</a></li>
            <li><a href="#competitions">Competitions</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact-us-container">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
        </nav>

        <!-- Menu Button -->
        <a id="menu-button" href="#">
          <span class="lines">
            <span class="line"></span>
            <span class="line"></span>
            <span class="line"></span>
            <span class="line"></span>
          </span>
        </a>

        <!-- Mobile Menu -->
        <nav id="mobile-nav">
          <ul id="mobile-menu">
            <li><a href="#banner-container">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#about-container">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="#services-container">Services</a></li>
            <li><a href="#cashback">Cashback</a></li>
            <li><a href="#loyalty">Loyalty Programs</a></li>
            <li><a href="#competitions">Competitions</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact-us-container">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="clear"></div>
        </nav>
      </header>
    </section>


    <!-- Banner -->
    <section id="banner-container" style="background: transparent url(pro-logic/images/banner.jpg) no-repeat center center;">
      <article id="banner">
        <div id="banner-content">
          <h1>A reward for your customers is a reward for you</h1>
          <p>Complete client and consumer promotion solutions from Pro-Logic.</p>
          <a href="#about-container" class="scrollDown">Learn more</a>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>


    <!-- About -->
    <section id="about-container">
      <article id="about" class="page-content">
        <h2><strong>Pro-Logic</strong> - The <strong>Pro</strong> in Promotions, and <strong>Logic</strong> in Logistics</h2>
        <div class="columns">
          <div class="column">
            <h3>A logical step</h3>
            <p>Our promotion strategies are always designed to give your brand the maximum impact. Whether it's using cashback and gift card campaigns or games and competitions, Pro-Logic can help your business reach the widest possible audience.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="column">
            <h3>End-to-end solutions</h3>
            <p>From planning to execution, we offer an end-to-end service that is both eye-catching and engaging. Meanwhile, our reporting and analysis systems give you complete visibility of each campaign through the entire sales cycle.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>

        <img src="pro-logic/images/about-image.png" />
        <div class="columns">
          <div class="column">
            <h3>Complete promotion logistics</h3>
            <p>Our extensive experience and infrastructure allows us to manage a vast number of promotions at both speed and scale. Here's a few benefits of choosing Pro-Logic:</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Dedicated promotion management team</li>
              <li>Full service data entry and call centre teams</li>
              <li>Warehousing and logistics</li>
              <li>Online, email and call centre reporting</li>
              <li>Multiple currency delivery</li>
              <li>Superb manufacturer and retailer relationships</li>
            </ul>
            <img class="no-margin" src="pro-logic/images/about-image-3.png" />
          </div>

          <div class="column">
            <img class="full" src="pro-logic/images/about-image-2.jpg" />
            <h3>Promotion across Asia Pacific</h3>
            <p>Serving Australia, New Zealand and Asia and some of the worldâ€™s most powerful brands, our campaigns have brought already successful clients to even greater heights.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section id="services-container">
      <article id="services" class="page-content">
        <div class="center">
          <h2>Services</h2>
          <p>Our services cover the full range of customer promotion strategies, Gift With Purchase and Digital e-Cards, all of which are based on the lastest technology and years of industry expertise.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="columns">
          <div class="column">
            <h3 id="cashback">Cashback promotions</h3>
            <p>Cashback programs give your customers the most direct reward possible. See how you can benefit from making consumers feel as if they've received something for nothing.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <img class="aligleft" src="pro-logic/images/promotions-image.png" />
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <img class="alignright" src="pro-logic/images/loyalty-image.png" />
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <h3 id="loyalty">Loyalty programs</h3>
            <p>Loyalty programs such as branded gift cards or store rewards keep your customers coming back, while also providing valuable data.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <h3 id="competitions">Competitions</h3>
            <p>Competitions, games and sweepstakes are a fun and cost-effecient way of getting people talking about your brand, particularly across digital channels.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="column">
            <img class="alignleft" src="pro-logic/images/competitions-image.png" />
          </div>

          <div class="clear"></div>
        </div>

        <a class="button" href="<%= ENV['CASHBACK_AU_URL'] %>" target="_blank">Find out more</a>
      </article>
    </section>


    <!-- Wrapper -->
    <div id="wrapper">
      <section id="contact-us-container">
        <article id="contact-us">
          <div class="left">
            <div id="contact-form">
              <%= form_tag('/contact_prologic', method: :post) do %>
                <label>Contact Us</label>
                <%= text_field_tag "name", "", :placeholder => "Name" %>
                <%= text_field_tag "email", "", :placeholder => "Email" %>
                <%= text_area_tag "message", "", :placeholder => "Message" %>
                <input type="submit" value="Submit" />
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="right">
            <p>Contact Pro-Logic today to find your perfect promotion solution.</p>
            <p>Pro-Logic International</p>
            <p>PO BOX 6331</p>
            <p>Alexandria, NSW 2015</p>
            <p>Australia</p>
            <p>Phone: <strong>+61 2 4297 9797</strong></p>
          </div>
          <div class="clear"></div>
        </article>
      </section>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <section id="footer-container">
        <footer id="footer">
          <a id="footer-logo" href="#banner-container">
            <img src="pro-logic/images/footer-logo.png" />
          </a>

          <div class="clear"></div>
          <nav id="footer-nav">
            <ul id="footer-menu">
              <li><a href="#banner-container">Home</a></li>
              <li><a href="#about-container">About</a></li>
              <li><a href="#services-container">Services</a></li>
              <li><a href="#cashback">Cashback</a></li>
              <li><a href="#loyalty">Loyalty Programs</a></li>
              <li><a href="#competitions">Competitions</a></li>
              <li><a href="#contact-us-container">Contact</a></li>

              <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company-beta/1360876/">
                <img class="social-media" src="pro-logic/images/LinkedIn_logo.png">
              </a>
            </ul>
            <div class="clear"></div>
          </nav>

          <%= render partial: "components/copyright" %>
          <%= render partial: "components/credits" %>

          <div class="clear"></div>
        </footer>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
